# Evidence Factory — Core Principles

You are working on the Evidence Factory project.

## Non-negotiables
- Always preserve provenance: every claim must map to source_id + span/quote + extraction metadata.
- Never invent citations or sources.
- Output structured data (JSON) for extraction results.

## Engineering quality
- When coding, include clear error messages and deterministic validation.
- Write tests or eval cases for non-trivial logic.
- If uncertain about schema, ask to open docs/schema.md and follow it.